{"tid":2153442,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"日本鼻敏感藥","createTime":"2020-08-12T13:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T02:24:55.000Z","uid":296664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78cd66b3ebe25b68fe818f3c4afd80a81f13a71f","tid":2153442,"uid":296664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:52:37.000Z","msg":"​我女朋友一直都有鼻敏感，發作嘅時候佢會間唔中用下面呢隻噴霧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKSwbBV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKSwbBV.png&h=1c9d14ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排佢鼻敏感發作但差唔多用晒之前帶去日本嘅呢隻藥。<br />\n加上日本而家封緊關，藥又唔可以速遞過去，所以想問吓有冇巴絲知道日本邊到買到同一隻藥/有其他藥推介。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb55f2141dec74491069160df1723d78fbb6558e","tid":2153442,"uid":188129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c353ab3c38a26d5e84bcec015e777d4ccdd00217","tid":2153442,"uid":54460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/GoodSense-Allergy-Cetirizine-Tablets-Antihistamine/dp/B00G9E1GYA/ref=mp_s_a_1_3?dchild=1&amp;keywords=allergy&amp;qid=1594210984&amp;sr=8-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoodSense-Allergy-Cetirizine-Tablets-Antihistamine%2Fdp%2FB00G9E1GYA%2Fref%3Dmp_s_a_1_3%3Fdchild%3D1%26keywords%3Dallergy%26qid%3D1594210984%26sr%3D8-3&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=d9bb0957\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/GoodSense-Allergy-Cetirizine-Tablets-Antihistamine/dp/B00G9E1GYA/ref=mp_s_a_1_3?dchild=1&amp;keywords=allergy&amp;qid=1594210984&amp;sr=8-3</a>"},{"pid":"7261981e3399228404c7a4b5871de6daa4fe8ae5","tid":2153442,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"內舒拿，以前耳鼻喉科開俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkg